"{\"uid\": \"myrepublica.nagariknetwork.com-news-olympian-phelps-suspended-for-3-months-over-marijuana\", \"text\": \"Subscribe Now  KATHMANDU, Feb 6: The great swimming sensation and all time high Olympic gold medalist Michael Phelps was suspended from competition for three months by USA Swimming, the latest fallout from a photo that showed the Olympic great inhaling from a marijuana pipe.The Associated Press (AP) reported rfom Colorado Springs, Colorado that the US sport\\u00b4s national governing body also cut off its financial support to Phelps for the same three-month period, effective Thursday.\\\"This is not a situation where any anti-doping rule was violated, but we decided to send a strong message to Michael because he disappointed so many people, particularly the hundreds of thousands of USA Swimming member kids who look up to him as a role model and a hero,\\\" the Colorado Springs-based federation said in a statement.Phelps won a record eight gold medals in Beijing and returned to America as one of the world\\u00b4s most acclaimed athletes. Now he\\u00b4s enduring a wave of bad news in the wake of the photo, published Sunday by News of the World, a British tabloid.Earlier Thursday, cereal and snack maker Kellogg Co. announced it wouldn\\u00b4t renew its sponsorship contract with Phelps, saying his behavior is \\\"not consistent with the image of Kellogg.\\\" The swimmer appeared on the company\\u00b4s cereal boxes after his Olympic triumph.(Read more in our \\u00b4Sports\\u00b4 section.)  Ballot Box Revolt: What RSP's breakthrough victory...  Warning, Threat or Opportunity? Nepal's major part...  Granary in crisis: Water politics leave Madhesh pa...  \\\"China stands ready to work with Nepal to carry forward the traditional friendship, deepen practical cooperation and advance bilateral relations\\\", read the statement.  Building Nepal's Digital Future  Fuel shortages in Nepal: A hidden threat to health a...  Second Innings of Balen and Gagan  Who will b